				<td colspan="2"><span>Yes Yes Yes, I have been trying to figure out what happened with this.  Ever since the patch of the 14th?  when they changed the aa system, I have noticed this.  I chant kite occasionally in HoH with my wizard BoT.  I have a pattern where I chant until 92% then nuke, and nuke each consecutive loop.  Since that patch I had to change to a lower level spell, AND wait until 85% to cast, then I have to concussion after every second cast in order not to get agro.  I am doing way more damage with my chants than with the nukes, but if I cast 3 in a row with the wizard bing he gets agro.  I do 161 each with my chants, and the wizard is now using Ice Spear of Solist which is a level 60 nuke and a 12 second recast.  I cant cast even one SoS without getting agro.
<br />

<br />
I wasnt sure what the problem was.  I figure it was they changed agro code in HoH, Increased agro of wizard spells across the board, or reduced the agro of Chants.  Based on what I am reading here, I would say they dramatically reduced the agro of chants.
<br />

